{"tid":1309811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩人權組織去信警區指揮官 促正視濫權","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:27:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f87ddf1e452c11b65596221e204ecc1567919c5","tid":1309811,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織香港分會及民權觀察，今日去信全港各警區指揮官，呼籲警方尊重集會自由，履行協助及配合市民和平集會及表達意見的責任，並促請警方正視處理遊行集會時濫權等問題，並作出實質改善。<br />\n<br />\n兩組織又指出，明白在政治爭議中，警方難免成為市民與政府間磨心，期望警方在執行職務時能專業克制，讓現時高度緊張的警民關係得以緩和。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190392/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2190392%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=3afa68a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190392/</a>"},{"pid":"e5f321a15280652b5c9343657bd42d95b60500a4","tid":1309811,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持獨立思考 唔好比敵人 輕易帶風向帶走左</span></span>"},{"pid":"d07e164e0222b0eb7237dfa6f324d1d1b914b366","tid":1309811,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"希望有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2f7fc975dd0f1616b874e6f4c8c28d28b82355","tid":1309811,"uid":261699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d07e164e0222b0eb7237dfa6f324d1d1b914b366","tid":1309811,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"希望有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"以呢個月嚟情況睇<br />\n我唔覺得有用<br />\n班毅進仔已經視香港議員無到<br />\n連英國國會都夠膽寫信去要求人地道歉<br />\n呢啲無實際權力嘅組織佢地邊會聽"}]}